                color: Colors.blue,
                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(10.0),
              ),
              child: Align(
                alignment: Alignment.center,
                child: Text(
                  '''
                  안녕하세요.
                  계정을 생성해주세요!
                  ''',
                  textAlign: TextAlign.center,
                  style: TextStyle(
                    fontSize: 22,
                    color: Colors.white,
                  ),
                ),
              ),
            ),
            SizedBox(
              height: 100,
            ),
            Column(
              children: <Widget>[
